Understanding these concepts is fundamental to writing correct and well-structured HTML. They form the basis for creating any webpage.


This list covers the major and most commonly used HTML tags. There are other tags, but these are the ones you'll encounter most frequently and are essential for building basic web pages. Remember to use these tags semantically, meaning use them for their intended purpose to create well-structured and accessible HTML.
